Script,PlayTopTricksNT
window.currentPBSScenario = 'PlayTopTricksNT';
window.currentPBSScenarioFilename = 'Play_Top_Tricks_NT';
console.log('PBS: Logging scenario selection for PlayTopTricksNT');
fetch('https://bba.harmonicsystems.com/api/scenario/select', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
        'X-Client-Version': '1.0.0'
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        scenario: 'PlayTopTricksNT',
        user: whoAmI() || 'anonymous'
    })
}).then(function(r){ console.log('PBS: Server response', r.status); }).catch(function(e){ console.log('PBS: Fetch error', e); });
setDealerCode(`

/*
convention-card-ns: Basic-Bridge
convention-card-ew: Basic-Bridge
auction-filter: Auction.....\n1N +Pass +2N +Pass\nPass +Pass
*/
##### Imported Script -- GIB 1 Notrump #####

# GIB opens 1N w/15-17 HCP or 15-16 and a 5-card major
ntP = hcp(south) + shape(south,5xxx+x5xx)
nt1 = shape(south, any 5332+any 4432+any 4333) and hcp(south)>14 and ntP<18

# GIB does not open with 5422 and a 5-card major or with 4 spades
# GIB does not open with 5422 and the strength to reverse
nt2 = shape(south, any 5422-5xxx-x5xx-4xxx) and hcp(south)>14 and hcp(south)<17

gibNT = nt1 or nt2

### End of GIB 1 Notrump ###
# Provides gibNT for South's 1NT opening (15-17 balanced).

# Opener — 1NT: 15-17 HCP, balanced, no 5-card major
sOpens = gibNT

# Responder — 8-9 HCP balanced, no 4-card major (no Stayman),
# no 5-card suit (no transfer). Just a flat raise to 2NT.
nShape = shape(north, any 4333 + any 4432) and spades(north) < 4 and hearts(north) < 4
nHcp   = hcp(north) > 7 and hcp(north) < 10

# All four Aces in NS — guarantees 4 quick tricks
nsAllAces = (hascard(south, AS) or hascard(north, AS))
        and (hascard(south, AH) or hascard(north, AH))
        and (hascard(south, AD) or hascard(north, AD))
        and (hascard(south, AC) or hascard(north, AC))

# Quiet opponents
eHcp = hcp(east) < 11
wHcp = hcp(west) < 11

sOpens and nShape and nHcp and nsAllAces and eHcp and wHcp

action printoneline,
average "South HCP avg "       hcp(south),
average "North HCP avg "       hcp(north),
average "NS combined  "        hcp(south) + hcp(north),
`, "S", true)
Script
Button,Top Tricks (NT),\n\
--- Top Tricks — Notrump Contract (beginner)\n\
1NT — Pass — 2NT — all pass. Final contract is 2NT (declarer needs 8 tricks).\n\
\n\
Teaching feature: NS holds ALL FOUR ACES (4 quick tricks). Add the 4\n\
kings (which the partnership also tends to have at 23-25 HCP) for 4\n\
more quick tricks — 8 total — and the contract makes on top tricks\n\
without needing any finesse.\n\
\n\
Responder is constrained to have NO 4-card major and NO 5-card suit so\n\
Stayman and transfers don't apply. The auction stays natural.\n\
\n\
Things to think about:\n\
• Count your top tricks before you touch the hand.\n\
• AKs in 3 or 4 suits add up fast in 1NT — 3NT contracts.\n\
• If you have 8 top tricks，cash them; don't finesse unnecessarily.\n\
\n\
Reference: https://www.bridgebum.com/counting.php\n\
%PlayTopTricksNT%
